{"_id":"4gjBRl2T22GV3iMC","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"Like any respectable sorceress, I carry my trusty bag full of herbs, poisons, and all kinds of magic tools. My childlike appearance is often useful, but sometimes it leads others to underestimate me. I hate that.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"Like any respectable sorceress, I carry my trusty bag full of herbs, poisons, and all kinds of magic tools. My childlike appearance is often useful, but sometimes it leads others to underestimate me. I hate that.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"L7O1ezrIll3E195s","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"My presence intimidates people, touching the fear that dwells deep in their hearts. The presence of children and their innocent way of looking at the world makes me uneasy.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"My presence intimidates people, touching the fear that dwells deep in their hearts. The presence of children and their innocent way of looking at the world makes me uneasy.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.babai-the-judge"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"3ConSe0D2DgaQAHH","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"Like it or not, we are bound by magic. We can share thoughts, each see what the other sees, and thanks to this we can work together to cheat others. Whoever is in animal form hates not being able to communicate and often annoys the other out of spite.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Like it or not, we are bound by magic. We can share thoughts, each see what the other sees, and thanks to this we can work together to cheat others. Whoever is in animal form hates not being able to communicate and often annoys the other out of spite.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"khTJtje3L5vNVALW","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I am fiercer and more powerful than any human and my fangs can pierce even metal. My proud wolf spirit is everything to me.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I am fiercer and more powerful than any human and my fangs can pierce even metal. My proud wolf spirit is everything to me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.garou-the-old-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"iIq0cXGarCpvOfjx","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I am a saint in the eyes of ordinary people and no door remains closed for me. My word is that of the Church itself. What I say is not to be questioned.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I am a saint in the eyes of ordinary people and no door remains closed for me. My word is that of the Church itself. What I say is not to be questioned.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"w3wtU6GHaC3Am1te","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I am a man of the world and nothing can really surprise me anymore. I never question myself. After all, I’m the best at what I do.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am a man of the world and nothing can really surprise me anymore. I never question myself. After all, I’m the best at what I do.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.james-the-swordsman"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"2hZ4nkOQm1FMczAH","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I have a massive collection of magical relics and treasures. I am very stingy with my collection and constantly seeking to add to my wealth so I can redeem my freedom.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I have a massive collection of magical relics and treasures. I am very stingy with my collection and constantly seeking to add to my wealth so I can redeem my freedom.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.marina-the-sea-explorer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Ivh0kypSdWvqLsHX","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"The demon in me grants me its power, allowing me to act with savage strength and speed. It is not easy to contain this ferocity and, often, I end up hurting or destroying things I did not wish to.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"The demon in me grants me its power, allowing me to act with savage strength and speed. It is not easy to contain this ferocity and, often, I end up hurting or destroying things I did not wish to.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.niklaus-von-krampus"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"4Sl56nxGWNNjFFAP","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I have an enviable charm and love to dress up to fit the role I have chosen. Even when I try to restrain myself, I never go unnoticed.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I have an enviable charm and love to dress up to fit the role I have chosen. Even when I try to restrain myself, I never go unnoticed.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.regina-the-thief-of-hearts"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"9TWPKlV3psYnuThW","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"My essence is magical, and this makes me resistant to enchantments that might snare stupid humans. My spiritual presence is imposing, and I struggle to hide what I am, especially in the eyes of those accustomed to magic.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"My essence is magical, and this makes me resistant to enchantments that might snare stupid humans. My spiritual presence is imposing, and I struggle to hide what I am, especially in the eyes of those accustomed to magic.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"xfJfFQfgk4rqz3Nn","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"As an artist I have traveled to many places and I know many myths and legends. I’m hungry for knowledge and I’m fascinated by everything I don’t know.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"As an artist I have traveled to many places and I know many myths and legends. I’m hungry for knowledge and I’m fascinated by everything I don’t know.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"plMcB5kxDsa4ji8c","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.the-woman-from-the-woods","ownerKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I love human flesh and can gain insight about people just looking at them. I am helplessly attracted to those who have a particular physical trait that stimulates my appetite, such as a good smell or velvety skin.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"I love human flesh and can gain insight about people just looking at them. I am helplessly attracted to those who have a particular physical trait that stimulates my appetite, such as a good smell or velvety skin.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.the-woman-from-the-woods"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ygOXscNR8AF8jgbt","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"My body is but a tool which I can manipulate at will, far beyond common human limits. In spite of my old and emaciated appearance, I feel neither fatigue nor pain. With matters of the flesh no longer of concern, I value beautiful things and works of art above anything else.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"My body is but a tool which I can manipulate at will, far beyond common human limits. In spite of my old and emaciated appearance, I feel neither fatigue nor pain. With matters of the flesh no longer of concern, I value beautiful things and works of art above anything else.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.theimmortal"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Lf0goSLVIuWIduYw","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"Under the facade of a respectable man hides a skilled, unscrupulous problem-solver. I know how to kill and how to act with decisiveness. Everyone has done something they are not proud of and I can’t stand seeing the hypocrites who pretend as if they are morally superior to others.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","positive":"Under the facade of a respectable man hides a skilled, unscrupulous problem-solver. I know how to kill and how to act with decisiveness. Everyone has done something they are not proud of and I can’t stand seeing the hypocrites who pretend as if they are morally superior to others.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"QT1PA6i9QJnFQ0C7","name":"Dark Ego Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-darkego.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"dark-ego-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"My body is pure ice and, because of this, I can manipulate ice as I please. However, I hate to manifest my power because it is dangerous to those around me and, as an artist, my purpose is to make people smile.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","positive":"My body is pure ice and, because of this, I can manipulate ice as I please. However, I hate to manifest my power because it is dangerous to those around me and, as an artist, my purpose is to make people smile.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-darkego.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"QpTgAgFaNGEu82d0","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I am a child witch, and my power is equal only to my ambition. I did not have a childhood, for I was born already aware of my abilities. To most, I seem cynical and cruel. That is because they do not understand that they are pawns, insignificant pieces in the bloody games that witches and warlocks play. The Order does not look down on my age, which is why it has given me the leadership I deserve.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a child witch, and my power is equal only to my ambition. I did not have a childhood, for I was born already aware of my abilities. To most, I seem cynical and cruel. That is because they do not understand that they are pawns, insignificant pieces in the bloody games that witches and warlocks play. The Order does not look down on my age, which is why it has given me the leadership I deserve.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"SoKNyzb5zMqYFiuA","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"After years of honorable service as State Inquisitor of the Republic of Venice, my body and spirit have undergone a rare mutation and fear is now unknown to me. People have always called me Bogeyman, fearing the justice that I represented. Perhaps my own absence of fear made me even more terrifying in the eyes of mortals. The Order has given me a new assignment because even in the fight against darkness, someone needs to be ready to judge what is right and what is wrong.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"After years of honorable service as State Inquisitor of the Republic of Venice, my body and spirit have undergone a rare mutation and fear is now unknown to me. People have always called me Bogeyman, fearing the justice that I represented. Perhaps my own absence of fear made me even more terrifying in the eyes of mortals. The Order has given me a new assignment because even in the fight against darkness, someone needs to be ready to judge what is right and what is wrong.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.babai-the-judge"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"aGGXgbr4r7ocXiv4","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"We are two boys who survived and thrived on the street through trickery and deceit. Unfortunately, we made a terrible mistake by choosing a weird old lady as a mark. She turned out to be a goddamn witch. The witch cursed us… And from that day on, every twelve hours, one becomes a Fox and the other a Cat. Bound by this spell, we found a way to make a lot of money, deceiving stupid nobles and rich merchants. The Order has noticed us and taken us under its wing, with the promise of breaking the curse that afflicts us.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"We are two boys who survived and thrived on the street through trickery and deceit. Unfortunately, we made a terrible mistake by choosing a weird old lady as a mark. She turned out to be a goddamn witch. The witch cursed us… And from that day on, every twelve hours, one becomes a Fox and the other a Cat. Bound by this spell, we found a way to make a lot of money, deceiving stupid nobles and rich merchants. The Order has noticed us and taken us under its wing, with the promise of breaking the curse that afflicts us.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"swezn8BMBBnIZThV","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I am a mountain wolf and far more cunning than the stupid villagers who tremble at the mere sight of me. I have lived proudly at the head of my pack, leading a thousand raids and eating succulent, tender morsels of human flesh. But I am not so old I cannot face those who hate me the most, though I may be hunted and reviled. Now that I’m part of the Order, I use my strength to defend the weak hunters who are my companions, knowing that with a single bite I could end their insignificant lives.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"I am a mountain wolf and far more cunning than the stupid villagers who tremble at the mere sight of me. I have lived proudly at the head of my pack, leading a thousand raids and eating succulent, tender morsels of human flesh. But I am not so old I cannot face those who hate me the most, though I may be hunted and reviled. Now that I’m part of the Order, I use my strength to defend the weak hunters who are my companions, knowing that with a single bite I could end their insignificant lives.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.garou-the-old-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"wXG4Ju1hwoYVfMK0","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I am the most skilled and trusted agent of the Papacy and as such, it is my responsibility to make sure that the fight against darkness never falters. As a child, I fell into a river and almost drowned, but was saved by a creature that I later discovered was a dragon. When I grew up, I took holy vows and joined the Church. In doing so, I discovered that what I believed to be my savior was actually a creature of darkness, ready to steal my soul. I vowed to fight the darkness, suppressing the feeling of gratitude toward the dragon that saved me, which has always plagued me. Such weakness represents a crack through which evil could slither in. No mercy for monsters, no forgiveness for those who would join and serve the forces of evil.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I am the most skilled and trusted agent of the Papacy and as such, it is my responsibility to make sure that the fight against darkness never falters. As a child, I fell into a river and almost drowned, but was saved by a creature that I later discovered was a dragon. When I grew up, I took holy vows and joined the Church. In doing so, I discovered that what I believed to be my savior was actually a creature of darkness, ready to steal my soul. I vowed to fight the darkness, suppressing the feeling of gratitude toward the dragon that saved me, which has always plagued me. Such weakness represents a crack through which evil could slither in. No mercy for monsters, no forgiveness for those who would join and serve the forces of evil.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"oBnRzBLlOBjOWFzk","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I have been a lot of things in my life: ship captain, duellist of great renown, and lover of the most beautiful noblewomen. After years of successes and victories, a mysterious child defeated me with deception. This despicable boy led me into the lair of a dangerous beast and, after imprisoning me, left me to be eaten by the monster. I survived, though I lost a hand... I know for certain he who I seek is no human, and I joined the Order to hunt down the child I hate above all else, and thus have my revenge.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I have been a lot of things in my life: ship captain, duellist of great renown, and lover of the most beautiful noblewomen. After years of successes and victories, a mysterious child defeated me with deception. This despicable boy led me into the lair of a dangerous beast and, after imprisoning me, left me to be eaten by the monster. I survived, though I lost a hand... I know for certain he who I seek is no human, and I joined the Order to hunt down the child I hate above all else, and thus have my revenge.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.james-the-swordsman"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ZVRIUMALsQ5LZksI","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I am a traveler, and, over the years, I have visited every location known to man. Being a traveling merchant has allowed me to easily hide my talents as a witch from prying eyes. Year after year, I have accumulated all kinds of magical and mundane wealth. But the Order found me and forced me to sign the most one-sided contract of my entire career as a trader. Now I must put my skills and my charisma at the service of the Order, trying to earn as much as possible to redeem the enormous debt that they have made me incur through deceit.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I am a traveler, and, over the years, I have visited every location known to man. Being a traveling merchant has allowed me to easily hide my talents as a witch from prying eyes. Year after year, I have accumulated all kinds of magical and mundane wealth. But the Order found me and forced me to sign the most one-sided contract of my entire career as a trader. Now I must put my skills and my charisma at the service of the Order, trying to earn as much as possible to redeem the enormous debt that they have made me incur through deceit.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.marina-the-sea-explorer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"04xhCrcrobixW4N6","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I am a devoted clergyman who has always dedicated his life to helping others. Over the years I have become a talented exorcist and this vocation of mine led me to the remote village of Borgo Maleanime. There, I fought a particularly insidious demon, who concealed itself among the ranks of a gang of young thugs who merely pretended to be demons to scare people. It was a tough fight, but I finally got the better of the fiend. Or so I thought. Something in the exorcism did not go as expected and now the demon dwells inside me, sowing fear and pain whenever it re-emerges. The Order welcomed me into its ranks as an exorcist and I gladly accepted this role, with the hope that the missions entrusted to me would allow me to find a way to rid myself, once and for all, of that which hides within me.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am a devoted clergyman who has always dedicated his life to helping others. Over the years I have become a talented exorcist and this vocation of mine led me to the remote village of Borgo Maleanime. There, I fought a particularly insidious demon, who concealed itself among the ranks of a gang of young thugs who merely pretended to be demons to scare people. It was a tough fight, but I finally got the better of the fiend. Or so I thought. Something in the exorcism did not go as expected and now the demon dwells inside me, sowing fear and pain whenever it re-emerges. The Order welcomed me into its ranks as an exorcist and I gladly accepted this role, with the hope that the missions entrusted to me would allow me to find a way to rid myself, once and for all, of that which hides within me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.niklaus-von-krampus"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Q7ODOGHT5IRSzWeQ","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I was born to be a leader and I have always surrounded myself with faithful followers ready to satisfy my every whim. Lacking the benefit of noble birth, the power I held was pried from the hands of those less deserving to wield it, no matter the cost. I ruled armies of thugs, and broke the hearts of both men and women. After each conquest, I set out in search of a bigger challenge. Because there is still so much out there that should be rightfully mine, I always want more. The Order has given me a new purpose, a new perspective, and new creatures to enslave.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I was born to be a leader and I have always surrounded myself with faithful followers ready to satisfy my every whim. Lacking the benefit of noble birth, the power I held was pried from the hands of those less deserving to wield it, no matter the cost. I ruled armies of thugs, and broke the hearts of both men and women. After each conquest, I set out in search of a bigger challenge. Because there is still so much out there that should be rightfully mine, I always want more. The Order has given me a new purpose, a new perspective, and new creatures to enslave.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.regina-the-thief-of-hearts"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"yZXguvum1zHM800T","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I have no memory of my life before my captivity, although I often dream of the forests and snow-capped peaks of my beloved China. I grew up as a circus animal at London’s Royal Circus but, deep within I carry the conviction that I am destined for something else. I rebelled by killing all my captors, fleeing across a vast and labyrinthine city. When the Order reached me, I thought it was the end, but the Hunters took me with them as their guardian and defender. The more I live as a Hunter, the closer I draw to transcendence. Now I am aware that, someday, I will discover who I really am.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"I have no memory of my life before my captivity, although I often dream of the forests and snow-capped peaks of my beloved China. I grew up as a circus animal at London’s Royal Circus but, deep within I carry the conviction that I am destined for something else. I rebelled by killing all my captors, fleeing across a vast and labyrinthine city. When the Order reached me, I thought it was the end, but the Hunters took me with them as their guardian and defender. The more I live as a Hunter, the closer I draw to transcendence. Now I am aware that, someday, I will discover who I really am.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"YOrMShr5kOrjAmNq","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I have always made my art my reason for living. I can play so skillfully that it might as well be magic. I have learned to use the power of music to reach into the souls of both humans and animals. Unfortunately, I have lost count of the number of times I have performed dishonorable acts while pursuing the perfect melody. Having been guilty of various crimes and having taken revenge on those who mocked my sincere love for music, I serenely waited for my execution. The Order freed me in exchange for a promise to serve them and put my skills to work in the fight against Darkness. It was in the darkest moments that I glimpsed the perfect melody, so perhaps as a Hunter, I can find it and make it my own.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I have always made my art my reason for living. I can play so skillfully that it might as well be magic. I have learned to use the power of music to reach into the souls of both humans and animals. Unfortunately, I have lost count of the number of times I have performed dishonorable acts while pursuing the perfect melody. Having been guilty of various crimes and having taken revenge on those who mocked my sincere love for music, I serenely waited for my execution. The Order freed me in exchange for a promise to serve them and put my skills to work in the fight against Darkness. It was in the darkest moments that I glimpsed the perfect melody, so perhaps as a Hunter, I can find it and make it my own.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"shuvUSV86jddAi4P","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.the-woman-from-the-woods","ownerKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"My memory is gone. The first thing I remember is the Order finding me, wandering in the woods naked and covered in blood. I possess extraordinary strength and a feral instinct, such that any civilized society ought to chain me like a monster. I know that in my past is a sin so great, my memory could not bear the weight of it. But, I want to remember and perhaps by serving the Order I will be able to do so. I have a natural soft spot for children, and I can’t stand to see them get hurt. The Order uses me as a weapon in the most serious matters when it is necessary to act decisively and demonstrate that a Hunter is a force to be reckoned with.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"My memory is gone. The first thing I remember is the Order finding me, wandering in the woods naked and covered in blood. I possess extraordinary strength and a feral instinct, such that any civilized society ought to chain me like a monster. I know that in my past is a sin so great, my memory could not bear the weight of it. But, I want to remember and perhaps by serving the Order I will be able to do so. I have a natural soft spot for children, and I can’t stand to see them get hurt. The Order uses me as a weapon in the most serious matters when it is necessary to act decisively and demonstrate that a Hunter is a force to be reckoned with.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.the-woman-from-the-woods"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"jISMZdV1lVDclFIY","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I am a sorcerer who has found the key to immortality. Long life has only whetted my appetite for power and in its pursuit, I have been stained by every sin. The secret behind my unending existence is that I have hidden my soul, removing it from my body. Unfortunately, the Order found its hiding place and now it is held beyond my reach in a fortified church, leaving me no choice but to submit to their commands. Guilty of one thousand and one crimes, the Order demands I balance each with one thousand and one acts of virtue. According to those foolish preachers, they are leading me down the path of redemption. In truth, the Order treats me as a servant, giving to me only the most thankless tasks, knowing that I can not be subdued by death. I remain humble and silent, waiting for the day when I will discover where they have hidden my soul. Then I will unleash my revenge and annihilate the entire Papacy...","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I am a sorcerer who has found the key to immortality. Long life has only whetted my appetite for power and in its pursuit, I have been stained by every sin. The secret behind my unending existence is that I have hidden my soul, removing it from my body. Unfortunately, the Order found its hiding place and now it is held beyond my reach in a fortified church, leaving me no choice but to submit to their commands. Guilty of one thousand and one crimes, the Order demands I balance each with one thousand and one acts of virtue. According to those foolish preachers, they are leading me down the path of redemption. In truth, the Order treats me as a servant, giving to me only the most thankless tasks, knowing that I can not be subdued by death. I remain humble and silent, waiting for the day when I will discover where they have hidden my soul. Then I will unleash my revenge and annihilate the entire Papacy...","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.theimmortal"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"vNF86xgicyxSrM6h","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I am a French aristocrat, called upon by my sovereign to manage the most devious and disreputable matters. I have lived an unconventional life, between accomplishing impossible tasks and keeping unspeakable secrets. It has opened my eyes to the world beyond the prosaic limits to which most are accustomed. In an effort to escape my adventurous life, I have more than once tried to start a family. However, my efforts have always ended in ruin, a price I must pay for the secrets I keep. I have lost six lovers, each killed by enemies and dangers that I naively hoped I could exclude from my life. That is why I volunteered for the Order, took an oath to weed out the darkness in this world, and sought revenge for the lives that were stolen from me.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","positive":"I am a French aristocrat, called upon by my sovereign to manage the most devious and disreputable matters. I have lived an unconventional life, between accomplishing impossible tasks and keeping unspeakable secrets. It has opened my eyes to the world beyond the prosaic limits to which most are accustomed. In an effort to escape my adventurous life, I have more than once tried to start a family. However, my efforts have always ended in ruin, a price I must pay for the secrets I keep. I have lost six lovers, each killed by enemies and dangers that I naively hoped I could exclude from my life. That is why I volunteered for the Order, took an oath to weed out the darkness in this world, and sought revenge for the lives that were stolen from me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"BTLvdTBNqOxYt07B","name":"Descriptor 1","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor-principal.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"principal-descriptor","sequence":0}},"system":{"description":"I am a traveling artist who has known fame and honor in my homeland, Japan. That prestige meant nothing, however, when I found true love with Akihiro, son of a powerful noble family. When they forbade him from seeing me, we fled together to the remote region of Ezo. Even there we were not beyond the reach of Akihiro’s family and they pursued us into the high, snow-capped mountains. We had escaped every assassin, but could not outwit the snowstorm that trapped us. I survived, but only because Akihiro sacrificed the warmth of his life to save mine. But the cold has left me changed. It has become part of me and now the only thing that can make me feel warm is the hot blood of others. After taking revenge on all those who took Akihiro from me, I fled far away, using my talent for art to gain prestige and the protection of wealthy western nobles. Now, in the service of the Order, I save others from suffering the injustice that I have experienced, by punishing selfishness and wickedness.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","positive":"I am a traveling artist who has known fame and honor in my homeland, Japan. That prestige meant nothing, however, when I found true love with Akihiro, son of a powerful noble family. When they forbade him from seeing me, we fled together to the remote region of Ezo. Even there we were not beyond the reach of Akihiro’s family and they pursued us into the high, snow-capped mountains. We had escaped every assassin, but could not outwit the snowstorm that trapped us. I survived, but only because Akihiro sacrificed the warmth of his life to save mine. But the cold has left me changed. It has become part of me and now the only thing that can make me feel warm is the hot blood of others. After taking revenge on all those who took Akihiro from me, I fled far away, using my talent for art to gain prestige and the protection of wealthy western nobles. Now, in the service of the Order, I save others from suffering the injustice that I have experienced, by punishing selfishness and wickedness.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor-principal.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"jO3YDCjtoFzjk3Y0","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I am a sorceress and my magical powers allow me to do whatever I want. I need the right amount of time to cast my spells.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am a sorceress and my magical powers allow me to do whatever I want. I need the right amount of time to cast my spells.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"FIuZgXjddFAhDEk4","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I am good at understanding, evaluating, and grasping every hidden detail, which is why the Order wanted me as a judge. I am cold, methodical, and cannot stand when plans change abruptly.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"I am good at understanding, evaluating, and grasping every hidden detail, which is why the Order wanted me as a judge. I am cold, methodical, and cannot stand when plans change abruptly.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.babai-the-judge"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"pshoDoCU0hwvbUA1","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"Cunning's Descriptor: I have a natural talent for telling lies, which the Order often uses to its advantage. Despite my origins, I know a great deal about many things because lying requires planning and preparation.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Cunning's Descriptor: I have a natural talent for telling lies, which the Order often uses to its advantage. Despite my origins, I know a great deal about many things because lying requires planning and preparation.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"pfHYMfOaq00NjZ8J","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"My senses are unfailing. Nothing can escape my sense of smell and that is why the Order uses me as a guardian. I hate strong smells and loud noises because they feel like burning irons to acute senses.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"My senses are unfailing. Nothing can escape my sense of smell and that is why the Order uses me as a guardian. I hate strong smells and loud noises because they feel like burning irons to acute senses.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.garou-the-old-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"4OCrrV26B9D4ADio","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I have dedicated my life to slaying monsters and aberrations, honing my body and my skill for that purpose. My strict discipline makes me rarely inclined to forgive the mistakes of others.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I have dedicated my life to slaying monsters and aberrations, honing my body and my skill for that purpose. My strict discipline makes me rarely inclined to forgive the mistakes of others.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"FbRoxNfHphsyNXQd","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled swordsman and possess fine manners, which is why the Order considers me an excellent candidate to move among High Society. I love indulging in good food and dissolute company.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I am a skilled swordsman and possess fine manners, which is why the Order considers me an excellent candidate to move among High Society. I love indulging in good food and dissolute company.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.james-the-swordsman"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"u6wEMSSvu2Dswkjb","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I am a sea witch, and as such, I have the power to shape water and move it at will. I hate enclosed places, cut off from the presence of my beloved sea.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"I am a sea witch, and as such, I have the power to shape water and move it at will. I hate enclosed places, cut off from the presence of my beloved sea.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.marina-the-sea-explorer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"l68E99pdP9DGenIw","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled exorcist. I know how to identify and fight evil through prayer and the sacred arts. Despite what I am, I hate holy places and manifestations of faith and religion, as they cause the demon inside me to stir.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am a skilled exorcist. I know how to identify and fight evil through prayer and the sacred arts. Despite what I am, I hate holy places and manifestations of faith and religion, as they cause the demon inside me to stir.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.niklaus-von-krampus"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"7T6bK3BsEyh5DGbT","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I am determined to get what I want, and nothing will get in my way. I will kill, humiliate, or conquer anything that stands between me and my objective. As you can imagine, I sincerely hate being told no!","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"I am determined to get what I want, and nothing will get in my way. I will kill, humiliate, or conquer anything that stands between me and my objective. As you can imagine, I sincerely hate being told no!","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.regina-the-thief-of-hearts"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"40PqdB4fqPHs3Hrb","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled guardian. My body is strong and hardened, my senses sharp and alert. Years of captivity have made me submissive, and I struggle not to follow every order I am given.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"I am a skilled guardian. My body is strong and hardened, my senses sharp and alert. Years of captivity have made me submissive, and I struggle not to follow every order I am given.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"CD4xvppWZDR7UOmP","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"With my pipe I can play any melody and touch the hearts of living beings. Art needs time to express itself.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"With my pipe I can play any melody and touch the hearts of living beings. Art needs time to express itself.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"MLzMtN038mhIemBa","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.the-woman-from-the-woods","ownerKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I am incredibly strong. Despite my petite looks, I am tougher than the sturdiest of men. I struggle to control my strength and often end up damaging things unintentionally.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"I am incredibly strong. Despite my petite looks, I am tougher than the sturdiest of men. I struggle to control my strength and often end up damaging things unintentionally.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.the-woman-from-the-woods"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"NNbXx6HnyuKUUBnj","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I have knowledge and wisdom drawn from centuries of existence, which I can conjure to mind when needed. I often get lost in the memories of my past glories, forgetting about the world around me.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"I have knowledge and wisdom drawn from centuries of existence, which I can conjure to mind when needed. I often get lost in the memories of my past glories, forgetting about the world around me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.theimmortal"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"tTtwxG0vulYe2t7m","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"My specialty is problem solving and I have a talent for analyzing every situation, allowing me to find resources and discover clues. Managing danger requires calm and concentration, and so I hate acting precipitously.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","positive":"My specialty is problem solving and I have a talent for analyzing every situation, allowing me to find resources and discover clues. Managing danger requires calm and concentration, and so I hate acting precipitously.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"1EJlFTkhcY3fTnOs","name":"Descriptor 2","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor1-don1.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":1}},"system":{"description":"I am a highly skilled artist. Music, dance, and painting hold no mysteries for me. My otherworldly charm captivates ordinary people, always drawing attention to me.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","positive":"I am a highly skilled artist. Music, dance, and painting hold no mysteries for me. My otherworldly charm captivates ordinary people, always drawing attention to me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor1-don1.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"9mSUrCOOFkerpgAQ","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","ownerKey":"cazador.baba-yaga-the-child-witch","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I am very skilled at reading people, that is why the Order has chosen me as leader of the Hunters. I love manipulating people and I often do it merely to amuse myself.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 10.","positive":"I am very skilled at reading people, that is why the Order has chosen me as leader of the Hunters. I love manipulating people and I often do it merely to amuse myself.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Baba yaga The Child Witch","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.baba-yaga-the-child-witch"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241638,"modifiedTime":1783973241638,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"9RlXXxhn8ePao4aj","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.babai-the-judge","ownerKey":"cazador.babai-the-judge","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"My body is made of pure shadow and I can become intangible for brief moments. I hate sunlight and cannot properly focus when not surrounded by a comforting shadow.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 14.","positive":"My body is made of pure shadow and I can become intangible for brief moments. I hate sunlight and cannot properly focus when not surrounded by a comforting shadow.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Babai the Judge","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.babai-the-judge"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"4bx1MV4D1tjUluDx","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Sly's Descriptor: A life on the road has taught me to be a skilled thief. Everyone for themselves is my motto.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Sly's Descriptor: A life on the road has taught me to be a skilled thief. Everyone for themselves is my motto.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"UtFN1p2V3bBjvLMe","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.garou-the-old-wolf","ownerKey":"cazador.garou-the-old-wolf","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"A true predator knows how to appear as the most helpless of lambs. I know how to disguise myself. My confidence is boundless and I often tend to underestimate danger, ready to risk anything for a tasty bite.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 6.","positive":"A true predator knows how to appear as the most helpless of lambs. I know how to disguise myself. My confidence is boundless and I often tend to underestimate danger, ready to risk anything for a tasty bite.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Garou the Old Wolf","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.garou-the-old-wolf"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"8tq5ea631EDCulS0","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","ownerKey":"cazador.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I have vowed to eradicate all evil from this world and nothing can escape my inquisitive gaze. I hate all secrets, for I know that the seed of evil may grow within anyone.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 24.","positive":"I have vowed to eradicate all evil from this world and nothing can escape my inquisitive gaze. I hate all secrets, for I know that the seed of evil may grow within anyone.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"George the Holy Dragon Slayer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.george-the-holy-dragon-slayer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"voh4Dv5hlkyFqea1","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.james-the-swordsman","ownerKey":"cazador.james-the-swordsman","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I have learned to face monsters and aberrations without being intimidated. The Beast is on my trail because, having tasted my flesh, it can no longer do without it…","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 4.","positive":"I have learned to face monsters and aberrations without being intimidated. The Beast is on my trail because, having tasted my flesh, it can no longer do without it…","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"James the Swordsman","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.james-the-swordsman"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241636,"modifiedTime":1783973241636,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"sR0shGRyDLFeDv61","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.marina-the-sea-explorer","ownerKey":"cazador.marina-the-sea-explorer","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Nobody knows my true form, which I hide under an appearance of eternal youth. I can change shape to some extent, while still remaining in human form. I am hopelessly attracted to all forms of beauty and I often get lost in contemplating it.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 20.","positive":"Nobody knows my true form, which I hide under an appearance of eternal youth. I can change shape to some extent, while still remaining in human form. I am hopelessly attracted to all forms of beauty and I often get lost in contemplating it.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Marina the Sea Explorer","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.marina-the-sea-explorer"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ci9rCgfmvvzwAd8f","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.niklaus-von-krampus","ownerKey":"cazador.niklaus-von-krampus","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I am good at understanding people and helping them. Now, thanks to the demon that dwells in me, I can even perceive the dark side of people. Every so often, however, the demon takes over, making me behave strangely in front of ordinary people.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 22.","positive":"I am good at understanding people and helping them. Now, thanks to the demon that dwells in me, I can even perceive the dark side of people. Every so often, however, the demon takes over, making me behave strangely in front of ordinary people.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Niklaus von Krampus","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.niklaus-von-krampus"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241641,"modifiedTime":1783973241641,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"MHmRt7uCCq7HGsC8","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","ownerKey":"cazador.regina-the-thief-of-hearts","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Thanks to my contacts and charisma, I always have an ace up my sleeve: followers ready to help me and allies who owe me favors. Maintaining an empire of beneficial connections requires commitment and resources.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 12.","positive":"Thanks to my contacts and charisma, I always have an ace up my sleeve: followers ready to help me and allies who owe me favors. Maintaining an empire of beneficial connections requires commitment and resources.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Regina The Thief Of Hearts","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.regina-the-thief-of-hearts"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241639,"modifiedTime":1783973241639,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"G5DOeLCqb9BvDhqp","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","ownerKey":"cazador.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I am stronger and faster than any human and I am a highly skilled fighter. I don’t shy away from a challenge because I always believe I can win.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 26.","positive":"I am stronger and faster than any human and I am a highly skilled fighter. I don’t shy away from a challenge because I always believe I can win.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Sun Wukong the Amazing Monkey","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.sun-wukong-the-amazing-monkey"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241642,"modifiedTime":1783973241642,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"vNRlSVZvG5vwJ74V","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","ownerKey":"cazador.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I am a skilled acrobat and musician. My talent is unrivaled and the Order has chosen me for my ability to capture people’s attention and stimulate their emotions. When I am in the grip of artistic inspiration, I am totally divorced from reality.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 8.","positive":"I am a skilled acrobat and musician. My talent is unrivaled and the Order has chosen me for my ability to capture people’s attention and stimulate their emotions. When I am in the grip of artistic inspiration, I am totally divorced from reality.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Astonishing Pied Piper Without a Name","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.the-astonishing-pied-piper-without-a-name"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241637,"modifiedTime":1783973241637,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"sZjlIKBPJPoWB4ir","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.the-woman-from-the-woods","ownerKey":"cazador.the-woman-from-the-woods","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"Sometimes I manifest strange abilities, the legacy of a past that I no longer remember. But, when I need it, the world around me shapes itself to protect and shelter me. I hate being out in the open and being the center of attention.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 16.","positive":"Sometimes I manifest strange abilities, the legacy of a past that I no longer remember. But, when I need it, the world around me shapes itself to protect and shelter me. I hate being out in the open and being the center of attention.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"The Woman from the Woods","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.the-woman-from-the-woods"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"oIFu1Kyh9ZZtEqpn","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.theimmortal","ownerKey":"cazador.theimmortal","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"The Order uses my powers for their own purposes and I have had to become skilled at understanding and supporting the needs of my allies as a result. Although I hate to admit it, over time I have begun to take some pleasure in doing good deeds.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 18.","positive":"The Order uses my powers for their own purposes and I have had to become skilled at understanding and supporting the needs of my allies as a result. Although I hate to admit it, over time I have begun to take some pleasure in doing good deeds.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"TheImmortal","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.theimmortal"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241640,"modifiedTime":1783973241640,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"AWGAOp4Xnj0phGin","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.verdoux-bluebeard","ownerKey":"cazador.verdoux-bluebeard","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I am an educated man who has studied the arts and sciences. I use this knowledge to uncover truths and reveal mysteries. I hate secrets, but only when I don’t know them.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 28.","positive":"I am an educated man who has studied the arts and sciences. I use this knowledge to uncover truths and reveal mysteries. I hate secrets, but only when I don’t know them.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Verdoux Bluebeard","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.verdoux-bluebeard"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"NKohhxMS5ipAyO2h","name":"Descriptor 3","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor2-don2.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","ownerKey":"cazador.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":2}},"system":{"description":"I cannot feel pain and my frail appearance hides surprising physical abilities. Blood is the only thing that can warm me and its smell alone makes me shiver.","notes":"See bt-cb-sheets-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 30.","positive":"I cannot feel pain and my frail appearance hides surprising physical abilities. Blood is the only thing that can warm me and its smell alone makes me shiver.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Yukie Onn the Traveling Artist","source":"Core Book","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor2-don2.yukie-onn-the-traveling-artist"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241643,"modifiedTime":1783973241643,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"KCK7xOo63OhzOq3Z","name":"Descriptor 4","type":"descriptor","img":"systems/broken-tales/assets/icons/descriptor-improvement.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","contentKey":"descriptor3-don3.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","ownerKey":"cazador.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat","role":"gift-descriptor","sequence":3}},"system":{"description":"Common Descriptor: I will stop at nothing to get what I want, and it only takes me a few seconds to evaluate what is happening and find the right way to take advantage of it. I hate acting alone because there's no one to take the blame.","notes":"See bt-cb-foxcat-sheet-eng-final-screen [2022-06-29].pdf, pages 2.","positive":"Common Descriptor: I will stop at nothing to get what I want, and it only takes me a few seconds to evaluate what is happening and find the right way to take advantage of it. I hate acting alone because there's no one to take the blame.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false,"owner":"Cunning Machiavelli the Fox and Sly Bischeri the Cat","source":"Core Book: Fox and Cat","category":"hunter","key":"descriptor3-don3.cunning-machiavelli-the-fox-and-sly-bischeri-the-cat"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1783973241644,"modifiedTime":1783973241644,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
